<hgroup class='page-header'>
<h2>
Archives for
June 2018
</h2>
</hgroup>
<div class='wrapper'>
<div class='story-stream'><div class='article-container' id=''><article class='clearfix post sharable short'><div class='article-img-container'>
<a href='https://mashable.com/2018/06/11/last-of-us-part-2-e3-2018-gameplay-trailer/'>

</a>
</div>
<div class='article-content-wrapper'>
<div class='article-content'>
<header>
<a class='article-category' href='#'>Entertainment</a>
<h2 class='article-title'>
<a href='https://mashable.com/2018/06/11/last-of-us-part-2-e3-2018-gameplay-trailer/'>
'The Last of Us Part II' offers a tender, brutal look at humanity, as you'd expect, at E3 2018
</a>
</h2>
</header>
<footer>
<div class='article-byline'><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Adam Rosenberg</span></div>
<time class='article-date' datetime='Tue, 12 Jun 2018 01:25:21 +0000'>
about 2 years ago
</time>
</footer>
<p class='article-excerpt'>&#39;The Last of Us Part II&#39; comes to E3 2018 with a look at familiar gameplay and equally familiar narrative gut punches.</p>
</div>
</div></article></div><div class='article-container' id=''><article class='clearfix post sharable short'><div class='article-img-container'>
<a href='https://mashable.com/2018/06/11/ted-cruz-facebook-questions-taylor-swift/'>
<figure class='image'>
<picture>
<source sizes='200w' srcset='https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fcard%252Fimage%252F790468%252F91795cff-5f8c-47f9-b53b-2fcbfd81284e.jpg%252F200x115__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpg?signature=Y-Q8SY36TEAsF716lu5HZeWLZ54=&amp;source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com 200w' type='image/jpg'>
<img alt='Ted Cruz had some truly WTF questions for Facebook.' class='microcontent' data-fragment='lead-image' data-image='https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fcard%252Fimage%252F790468%252F91795cff-5f8c-47f9-b53b-2fcbfd81284e.jpg%252F950x534__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpg' data-micro='1' naturalWidth='200' sizes='200w' src='https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fcard%252Fimage%252F790468%252F91795cff-5f8c-47f9-b53b-2fcbfd81284e.jpg%252F950x534__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpg' src_type='jpg' srcset='https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fcard%252Fimage%252F790468%252F91795cff-5f8c-47f9-b53b-2fcbfd81284e.jpg%252F200x115__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpg?signature=Y-Q8SY36TEAsF716lu5HZeWLZ54=&amp;source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com 200w'>
</picture>
<figcaption class='image-caption'>
Ted Cruz had some truly WTF questions for Facebook.
</figcaption>
<div class='image-credit'>
Image:  Getty Images
</div>
</figure>


</a>
</div>
<div class='article-content-wrapper'>
<div class='article-content'>
<header>
